OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FAn inquest jury has found that
OL,7,Ffailures by medical professionals to
OL,8,Fidentify a 12-year-old girl's brain
OL,9,Fdisorder "possibly contributed" to her
OL,10,Fdeath at a mental health unit.
OL,12,FMia Lucas, from Nottingham, took her
OL,13,Fown life in January 2024 after being
OL,14,Fsectioned at the Becton Centre in
OL,15,FSheffield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/18
