OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FIt was only revealed part-way through
OL,7,Fa nine-day inquest in the city that
OL,8,Fshe had undiagnosed autoimmune
OL,9,Fencephalitis, a swelling of the brain,
OL,10,Fwhich caused her acute psychosis but
OL,11,Fcould have been treated.
OL,13,FOn Thursday, the jury found that the
OL,14,Ffailure by staff at the Queens Medical
OL,15,FCentre (QMC) in Nottingham to
OL,16,Fundertake a lumbar puncture before her
OL,17,Ftransfer to the Becton Centre
OL,18,F"possibly contributed to Mia's death".
