OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe jury also said there was a failure
OL,7,Fat the Becton Centre to respond
OL,8,Fadequately to Mia's risk of self-harm.
OL,10,FIn a statement after the conclusion of
OL,11,Fthe hearing, Mia's mother Chloe Hayes
OL,12,Fsaid she would never forgive those
OL,13,Finvolved.
OL,15,FShe said: "It has been devastating to
OL,16,Flisten to how, when she needed
OL,17,Fspecialist healthcare, for the first
OL,18,Ftime in her life, she was so badly let
OL,19,Fdown.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
