PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F364A1764350944
OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"She was let down at the Queen's
OL,7,FMedical Centre in Nottingham, who
OL,8,Fwrongly decided there was no
OL,9,Funderlying physical cause of her
OL,10,Fpsychosis, and failed to carry out
OL,11,Fappropriate testing.
OL,13,F"I believe they simply dismissed her
OL,14,Fand looked to pass her onto mental
OL,15,Fhealth services as quickly as
OL,16,Fpossible, which led to her transfer to
OL,17,Fthe Becton centre."
