OL,6,FThe inquest heard how Mia began to
OL,7,Fbehave strangely over Christmas 2023 `
OL,8,Fincluding hearing voices and attacking
OL,9,Fher mother.
OL,11,FHer family became so concerned she was
OL,12,Ftaken by ambulance to QMC on New
OL,13,FYear's Eve.
OL,15,FShe was found to be experiencing an
OL,16,F"acute psychotic episode" and was
OL,17,Fsectioned under the Mental Health Act.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@YO]
