OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe jury of five women and four men
OL,7,Fheard how blood tests and an MRI scan
OL,8,Fat QMC returned negative results and
OL,9,Fdoctors ruled out a physical cause of
OL,10,FMia's psychosis.
OL,12,FBut doctors at Nottingham decided not
OL,13,Fto order further tests on brain wave
OL,14,Ffunction and spinal fluid, through a
OL,15,Flumbar puncture, which may have
OL,16,Frevealed the autoimmune encephalitis,
OL,17,Fwhich is very rare.
OL,19,FMia was transferred to the Becton
OL,20,FCentre, which is part of Sheffield
OL,21,FChildren's Hospital, on 9 January.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/18
