OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FShe was found unresponsive in her room
OL,7,Fon 29 January.
OL,9,FMrs Hayes said the "many failings and
OL,10,Flack of care meant sadly she wasn't
OL,11,Fproperly protected from harming
OL,12,Fherself".
OL,14,FShe added: "My beautiful little girl
OL,15,Fhas lost her life and I will never
OL,16,Fforgive the Queen's Medical Centre or
OL,17,Fthe Becton Centre for failing her."
OL,26,@vD@LOUyD@cO]
