OL,6,FMrs Hayes said the Becton Centre
OL,7,F"proved to be completely unsuitable
OL,8,Ffor her, and one which failed to keep
OL,9,Fher safe".
OL,11,FShe said: "I have never believed for a
OL,12,Fmoment that Mia ever wanted to take
OL,13,Fher own life. She was always a happy,
OL,14,Fhealthy child and had so much to live
OL,15,Ffor."
