OL,6,FMrs Hayes said she wanted everyone to
OL,7,Fknow that Mia's extreme behaviour was
OL,8,Fonly evident in the final few weeks of
OL,9,Fher life and "for the other 12 years,
OL,10,Fshe was a beautiful soul who loved
OL,11,Flife and loved her family, and that's
OL,12,Fhow we want her to be remembered".
OL,14,FShe said she was "happy, fun, friendly
OL,15,Fgirl who had so much to live for."
