OL,6,FIn a narrative conclusion, the jury
OL,7,Fsaid: "The failure to undertake a
OL,8,Flumbar puncture at this point (at QMC)
OL,9,Fmeant that potential indicators of
OL,10,Fautoimmune encephalitis were missed.
OL,12,F"This possibly contributed to Mia's
OL,13,Fdeath."
OL,15,FThe jury added that the information
OL,16,Fpassed between QMC and the Becton
OL,17,FCentre "provided an inappropriate
OL,18,Flevel of assurance that organic causes
OL,19,Fhad been ruled out".
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUuD@GO]yD@HOU{D@SO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/18
