OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FIn relation to the Becton Centre, the
OL,7,Fjury concluded that: "Insufficiently
OL,8,Frobust communication and management of
OL,9,Frisk led to a failure to respond
OL,10,Fadequately to Mia's risk of self-harm."
OL,12,FThe jury also said that a "rare
OL,13,Fpresentation of a rare condition"
OL,14,Fprovided "particularly complex
OL,15,Fchallenges" for diagnosis and care.
OL,26,@oD@VOUrD@gO]tD@[OUuD@aO]vD@JOUwD@KO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/18
