OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe jurors found, on the directions of
OL,7,Fthe senior Sheffield coroner Tanyka
OL,8,FRawden, that Mia's cause of death was
OL,9,F"compression of the neck", caused by
OL,10,F"acute psychosis", caused by
OL,11,F"autoimmune encephalitis".
OL,13,FThey heard how Mia self-harmed in her
OL,14,Fthree weeks at the Becton Centre, but
OL,15,Fthe coroner said there was not enough
OL,16,Fevidence for the jury to find staff
OL,17,Fhandovers on 29 January contributed to
OL,18,FMia's death.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@YO]rD@AOUrD@QO]sD@AOUsD@YO]
