OL,6,FMrs Rawden said she would write to
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting, along
OL,8,Fwith a number of professional bodies,
OL,9,Fabout her concerns about the lack of
OL,10,Fnational guidance over testing for
OL,11,Fautoimmune encephalitis.
OL,13,FShe said she was satisfied she did not
OL,14,Fneed to write to Sheffield Children's
OL,15,FHospital after hearing about a range
OL,16,Fof changes at the Becton Centre.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/18
