OL,6,FMrs Rawden said she would wait six
OL,7,Fmonths, to let Nottingham University
OL,8,FHospitals finish its own
OL,9,Finvestigation, before considering a
OL,10,Fletter to that trust.
OL,12,FMs Hayes's solicitor Amy Rossall, of
OL,13,FHudgell Solicitors, said: "We've heard
OL,14,Fmany comments about lessons being
OL,15,Flearned as a result of what happened
OL,16,Fto Mia, and those learnings will
OL,17,Fhopefully help to avoid other families
OL,18,Flosing their children to the
OL,19,Fcondition."
