OL,6,FIn a statement, Dr Manjeet Shehmar,
OL,7,Fmedical director at Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust (NUH),
OL,9,Fapologised to Mia's family "for not
OL,10,Fidentifying autoimmune encephalitis
OL,11,Fwhile she was in our care".
OL,13,FShe added: "While this is an
OL,14,Fincredibly rare condition and initial
OL,15,Ftests were negative, we recognise that
OL,16,Ffurther testing may have had an impact
OL,17,Fon her future, for which we are truly
OL,18,Fsorry.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G15/18
