OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F364A1764350944
OL,3,CFailure to spot brain disorder
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"We will take the feedback from the
OL,7,Finquest on board and in all future
OL,8,Fcases of suspected possible autoimmune
OL,9,Fencephalitis a lumbar puncture will be
OL,10,Fperformed, even in cases of atypical
OL,11,Fpresentation like Mia's.
OL,13,F"We will also strengthen training and
OL,14,Fguidance for staff internally and
OL,15,Freview current published evidence of
OL,16,Facute psychotic episodes in children
OL,17,Fand young people to support the
OL,18,Fdevelopment of clinical guidelines."
