OL,6,FDr Jeff Perring, executive medical
OL,7,Fdirector at Sheffield Children's NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, said a "thorough
OL,9,Freview" of Mia's care had been carried
OL,10,Fout and "significant changes" made.
OL,12,FHe added: "In September 2025 a Care
OL,13,FQuality Commission inspection at the
OL,14,FBecton Centre rated it as good. It
OL,15,Ffound the centre to be safe and staff
OL,16,Fthere caring and responsive to patient
OL,17,Fneeds.
