OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"We will continue to work with
OL,7,Fchildren, young people, their families
OL,8,Fand carers to listen to, learn and
OL,9,Ftake action from their experiences
OL,11,F"The inquest has been important to
OL,12,Funderstand fully the circumstances
OL,13,Fsurrounding Mia's death. We will now
OL,14,Fcarefully reflect on the evidence
OL,15,Fheard and the coroner's conclusions to
OL,16,Fensure we continue to provide safe and
OL,17,Fcompassionate care."
